OL,3,CSikh community secure first Gurdwara
OL,4,Cin Surrey after raising #1.5 million
OL,6,FThe Sikh community in Surrey is
OL,7,Ffinally on its way to having its first
OL,8,FGurdwara in the county, following a
OL,9,Ftwo-year campaign.
OL,11,FThe building in Camberley is a former
OL,12,FMinistry of Defence site and when it
OL,13,Fwent up for auction, everyone pulled
OL,14,Ftogether and were able to raise the
OL,15,F#1.5 million needed to buy it.
OL,17,FIt's a big step forward for the
OL,18,Fcommunity, who've been using local
OL,19,Fhalls and theatre for worship over the
OL,20,Flast 20 years.
