OL,6,FTheir growing numbers mean it's the
OL,7,Fperfect time for what will become, not
OL,8,Fonly a place or worship, but also a
OL,9,Fcommunity hub.
OL,11,FPlans to expand the outreach includes
OL,12,Fhospital pickups, Punjabi classes and
OL,13,Fsupport for the elderly and vulnerable.
OL,15,FDeepak Singh Udassi, GNGC Steering
OL,16,FCommittee, said: "If you can imagine
OL,17,Fit - births, deaths, weddings, big
OL,18,Foccasions - nothing being catered for
OL,19,Ffor the near enough 1500 Sikh families
OL,20,Fin the area.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
