OL,3,CSikh community secure first Gurdwara
OL,4,Cin Surrey after raising #1.5 million
OL,6,F"They were jumping on the train to
OL,7,FSouthampton or Southall, both of which
OL,8,Fare an hour and ten minutes away. So
OL,9,Fit was crying out for somewhere,
OL,10,Fsomething local, and now we have that."
OL,12,FKuldip Singh, GNGC Steering Committee,
OL,13,Fsaid: "What we are looking at is
OL,14,Fbuying a few vans and doing community
OL,15,Fwork, which we have been doing for 15
OL,16,Fyears.
