OL,6,F"It's feeding the homeless in
OL,7,FAldershot and places like that, and
OL,8,Frather than do one day, we want to try
OL,9,Fand hit three days a week. This will
OL,10,Fall be free for basically anybody,
OL,11,Fsomebody homeless or someone on low
OL,12,Fincome."
OL,14,FA memorial will be built at the
OL,15,FGurdwara, paying tribute to Sikhs who
OL,16,Ffought in WW1 and WW2.
