OL,3,CSikh community secure first Gurdwara
OL,4,Cin Surrey after raising #1.5 million
OL,6,FDr Al Pinkerton, MP Surrey Heath,
OL,7,Fsaid: "So many Sikhs have fought and
OL,8,Fdied for the British Army and now to
OL,9,Fthink that this building, that was
OL,10,Fpart of the MoD estate, is now going
OL,11,Fto be a Gurdwara, it's just a terrific
OL,12,Fcircularity and really shows how
OL,13,Fembedded the Sikh community are here
OL,14,Fin Surrey Heath."
OL,16,FIt's hoped it will take around three
OL,17,Fto four months for the Gurdwara become
OL,18,Fa reality, before the doors officially
OL,19,Fopen in April.
